Fire Department of Kingston, Respondent, v. Derrenbacher, Appellant, (three cases.) (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. September 25, 1891.) Actions by the Eire Department of "Kingston against John P. Derrenbacher.

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon, J.

. Ho opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements.
